{%- comment -%} Homepage Content - Uses Section Groups {%- endcomment -%}
{% sections 'index' %}

{% comment %}
  USAGE INSTRUCTIONS:
  
  This is a JSON template that uses Shopify's section groups.
  The actual sections are configured in templates/index.json
  
  To customize the homepage:
  1. Go to Online Store > Themes > Customize
  2. Navigate to Homepage
  3. Add/remove/reorder sections
  4. Configure each section's settings
  
  Available StyleDrop Sections:
  - Hero Section
  - Trending Products
  - Testimonials
  
  You can also add Dawn's built-in sections:
  - Image banner
  - Featured collection
  - Multicolumn
  - Newsletter
  - etc.
  
  RECOMMENDED HOMEPAGE STRUCTURE:
  1. Hero Section (custom)
  2. Trending Products (custom)
  3. Image banner (for lifestyle banners)
  4. Featured collection (for categories)
  5. Testimonials (custom)
  6. Newsletter (Dawn built-in)
{% endcomment %}

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Main Index",
  "settings": []
}
{% endschema %}
